and everything was in a mess.

572
00:36:35,420 --> 00:36:37,580
We planned to tell you
after the problem was solved.

573
00:36:37,740 --> 00:36:39,140
How can it be solved?

574
00:36:39,940 --> 00:36:41,820
She's in prison now.

575
00:36:42,980 --> 00:36:43,900
Oh my God.

576
00:36:44,540 --> 00:36:45,900
Haven't you asked around?

577
00:36:46,020 --> 00:36:47,860
What exactly happened?

578
00:36:48,940 --> 00:36:49,780
Mom,

579
00:36:49,900 --> 00:36:53,580
what could you do if we told you?

580
00:36:53,580 --> 00:36:54,420
I...

581
00:36:55,020 --> 00:36:56,660
We should do something

582
00:36:56,660 --> 00:36:58,700
to prove she's innocent.

583
00:36:58,700 --> 00:37:01,020
Mom, we're working on it.

584
00:37:03,220 --> 00:37:07,340
But if Jiahuan has really
done something wrong...

585
00:37:07,340 --> 00:37:08,900
She couldn't have done anything wrong.

586
00:37:08,940 --> 00:37:11,340
Among my daughters,

587
00:37:11,340 --> 00:37:12,380
she's the smartest one.

588
00:37:12,420 --> 00:37:13,820
How would she do anything so silly?

589
00:37:14,100 --> 00:37:15,340
Alright, Mom.

590
00:37:15,340 --> 00:37:17,140
Don't get too anxious.

591
00:37:17,140 --> 00:37:18,140
We'll think of a way.

592
00:37:18,140 --> 00:37:19,140
There are laws.

593
00:37:19,140 --> 00:37:20,580
The investigation takes some time.

594
00:37:20,580 --> 00:37:21,420
You knew that, too?

595
00:37:21,740 --> 00:37:22,620
I didn't know.

596
00:37:22,820 --> 00:37:24,220
Tao, you...

597
00:37:24,460 --> 00:37:25,940
You have many friends, don't you?

598
00:37:25,940 --> 00:37:26,780
Mom,

599
00:37:27,660 --> 00:37:29,420
I know all I need to know.

600
00:37:29,620 --> 00:37:30,460
Now,

601
00:37:31,220 --> 00:37:32,500
we can't do anything.

602
00:37:34,020 --> 00:37:35,340
That's too bad.

603
00:37:36,780 --> 00:37:37,620
Come on.

604
00:37:39,620 --> 00:37:40,460
Mom,

605
00:37:41,980 --> 00:37:43,580
most of the guests have left.

606
00:37:43,860 --> 00:37:46,780
This is the list of consolation money.

607
00:37:47,420 --> 00:37:48,260
And a ledger.

608
00:37:48,340 --> 00:37:49,740
I've kept clear records.

609
00:37:49,740 --> 00:37:50,580
Take a look.

610
00:37:53,220 --> 00:37:54,060
Here's the money.

611
00:38:04,820 --> 00:38:05,660
Jiayi!

612
00:38:07,140 --> 00:38:07,980
Jiaxi?

613
00:38:08,260 --> 00:38:09,100
Ouyang.

614
00:38:10,140 --> 00:38:12,220
- I have something to ask you.
- What is it?

615
00:38:12,220 --> 00:38:13,460
My mother-in-law's house.

616
00:38:13,660 --> 00:38:15,460
You said you would serve breakfast.

617
00:38:15,460 --> 00:38:17,060
Why are the walls being smashed?

618
00:38:18,060 --> 00:38:18,900
We...

619
00:38:19,940 --> 00:38:21,180
Let me explain.

620
00:38:21,380 --> 00:38:22,580
We did some research.

621
00:38:23,060 --> 00:38:23,940
The breakfast business

622
00:38:23,940 --> 00:38:24,780
is oversaturated.

623
00:38:25,020 --> 00:38:26,580
So, we will do another business.

624
00:38:27,060 --> 00:38:27,900
What business?

625
00:38:28,100 --> 00:38:29,220
- Hotel.
- Right.

626
00:38:29,940 --> 00:38:31,140
I don't approve, then.

627
00:38:31,780 --> 00:38:33,620
That'll be chaotic.

628
00:38:33,620 --> 00:38:35,420
But her family also did that business.

629
00:38:35,420 --> 00:38:36,660
Before I married Hongyu, anyway.

630
00:38:37,020 --> 00:38:38,380
If you run a hotel,

631
00:38:38,460 --> 00:38:40,140
all kinds of visitors will be messy.

632
00:38:40,140 --> 00:38:41,860
That's lawful. It won't be messy.

633
00:38:42,140 --> 00:38:42,980
Besides,

634
00:38:42,980 --> 00:38:43,860
you and hotel guests

635
00:38:43,860 --> 00:38:45,180
go through different doors.

636
00:38:45,620 --> 00:38:46,860
We won't disturb each other.

637
00:38:46,860 --> 00:38:47,700
Don't worry.

638
00:38:48,980 --> 00:38:50,980
(Grandma)
Good for you.

639
00:38:51,260 --> 00:38:52,100
Jiaxi,

640
00:38:53,260 --> 00:38:54,820
hide what you don't deserve.

641
00:38:55,620 --> 00:38:57,180
Don't be so blatant.

642
00:38:57,380 --> 00:38:59,180
(Grandma)
Or people will gossip.

643
00:39:04,220 --> 00:39:05,060
Honey,

644
00:39:05,700 --> 00:39:07,060
it's kind of hard

645
00:39:07,380 --> 00:39:08,740
to convince Jiaxi.

646
00:39:08,740 --> 00:39:10,140
It's ok. Don't worry about her.

647
00:39:10,620 --> 00:39:11,780
Did you see that?

648
00:39:11,780 --> 00:39:14,140
Mom gave her all the money so soon.

649
00:39:14,940 --> 00:39:15,780
What money?

650
00:39:15,780 --> 00:39:17,140
The envelope in her bag.

651
00:39:17,420 --> 00:39:18,260
Oh, it's Mom's.

652
00:39:19,380 --> 00:39:20,540
Don't think too much.

653
00:39:20,940 --> 00:39:22,980
That's not our money. No big deal.

654
00:39:23,940 --> 00:39:25,380
We helped with the funeral, too.

655
00:39:26,140 --> 00:39:28,380
And some of the money

656
00:39:28,380 --> 00:39:29,660
was from our friends.

657
00:39:29,820 --> 00:39:31,180
We'll give it back in future cases.

658
00:39:32,020 --> 00:39:33,020
Listen to me.

659
00:39:33,340 --> 00:39:34,180
Go ahead.

660
00:39:34,180 --> 00:39:35,420
Our hotel will be renovated.

661
00:39:36,140 --> 00:39:36,980
We also need money.

662
00:39:36,980 --> 00:39:37,980
Doesn't Mom know that?

663
00:39:38,380 --> 00:39:39,860
When Jiaxi opened a store,

664
00:39:39,860 --> 00:39:41,420
Mom must have given her a lot.

665
00:39:41,660 --> 00:39:42,660
Now, it goes again.

666
00:39:59,220 --> 00:40:05,220
(Freight transport and Removal Service)

667
00:40:09,060 --> 00:40:10,260
Nice hair color.

668
00:40:14,980 --> 00:40:16,540
I may hit you again.

669
00:40:16,740 --> 00:40:17,820
That's ok.

670
00:40:18,020 --> 00:40:19,580
But you must know how things are going.

671
00:40:20,620 --> 00:40:21,860
The situation is,

672
00:40:21,940 --> 00:40:23,180
Jiahuan's superior

673
00:40:23,180 --> 00:40:24,580
must have done something wrong.

674
00:40:24,820 --> 00:40:26,220
Two vice presidents and Jiahuan

675
00:40:26,220 --> 00:40:27,740
are suspected as accomplices.

676
00:40:27,740 --> 00:40:28,580
No way.

677
00:40:28,740 --> 00:40:30,220
She would never do anything like that.

678
00:40:30,220 --> 00:40:32,020
I know she wouldn't.

679
00:40:32,020 --> 00:40:33,980
And I'm sure she didn't do that.

680
00:40:34,380 --> 00:40:35,820
But we need proof.

681
00:40:36,980 --> 00:40:38,180
I have friends in the Procuratorate.

682
00:40:38,540 --> 00:40:40,020
I'm asking them to figure out more.

683
00:40:41,980 --> 00:40:44,180
I just want to know
when she can come out

684
00:40:44,780 --> 00:40:46,020
and when I can visit her.

685
00:40:46,220 --> 00:40:47,580
It's hard to tell now.

686
00:40:49,340 --> 00:40:50,180
By the way,

687
00:40:50,700 --> 00:40:51,860
the lawyer you have...

688
00:40:51,860 --> 00:40:53,060
He isn't capable enough.

689
00:40:53,140 --> 00:40:54,980
I'm going to get a lawyer from Hefei.

690
00:40:55,380 --> 00:40:56,220
Go ahead.

691
00:40:56,620 --> 00:40:57,580
Get the best one.

692
00:40:58,220 --> 00:40:59,180
I'll pay.

693
00:40:59,220 --> 00:41:00,380
Come on, man.

694
00:41:00,420 --> 00:41:02,380
Don't bother about money at this moment.

695
00:41:04,420 --> 00:41:05,260
I'm going.

696
00:41:12,620 --> 00:41:13,540
Qiulin.

697
00:41:15,280 --> 00:41:16,180
Thank you.

698
00:41:31,380 --> 00:41:32,220
Lunch is ready.

699
00:41:37,580 --> 00:41:38,420
Mom,

700
00:41:38,780 --> 00:41:39,820
let me tell you something.

701
00:41:42,460 --> 00:41:43,780
Don't be so serious.

702
00:41:44,020 --> 00:41:44,940
What is it?

703
00:41:53,140 --> 00:41:53,980
Really?

704
00:41:55,580 --> 00:41:57,180
That's awesome.

705
00:41:58,360 --> 00:41:59,220
How far along are you?

706
00:41:59,260 --> 00:42:00,140
Over a month.

707
00:42:00,780 --> 00:42:01,620
Jianguo.

708
00:42:02,180 --> 00:42:03,060
What are you talking about?

709
00:42:03,700 --> 00:42:04,660
Congratulations to Mom.

710
00:42:04,660 --> 00:42:05,980
She'll be a grandma.

711
00:42:06,780 --> 00:42:07,620
She's pregnant.

712
00:42:08,340 --> 00:42:09,980
That's great news.

713
00:42:09,980 --> 00:42:11,500
- Sit down.
- Come on, sit.

714
00:42:14,620 --> 00:42:15,620
This is so great.

715
00:42:17,780 --> 00:42:18,660
Eat more.

716
00:42:19,060 --> 00:42:20,180
You need well-balanced meals.

717
00:42:20,380 --> 00:42:21,660
Xiaonian, peel shrimp for her.

718
00:42:22,060 --> 00:42:22,900
Hurry.

719
00:42:24,180 --> 00:42:26,620
From now on, don't do any housework.

720
00:42:26,640 --> 00:42:27,780
Don't even wet your hands.

721
00:42:28,020 --> 00:42:29,380
Tell Mom whatever you want to eat.

722
00:42:30,090 --> 00:42:31,820
Mom, that's really sweet.

723
00:42:32,380 --> 00:42:34,460
She's going to have a very nice year.

724
00:42:34,460 --> 00:42:36,740
Of course, she will. Right?

725
00:42:36,980 --> 00:42:38,220
Yes. That's right.

726
00:42:38,820 --> 00:42:39,660
Very nice.

727
00:42:46,260 --> 00:42:47,100
Too bad.

728
00:42:48,100 --> 00:42:49,780
Your great-grandma can't see this day.

729
00:42:57,220 --> 00:42:59,540
She must be watching in heaven.

730
